we\nfind P3-K$_x$CoO$_2$ to be the most promising cathode composition, while\nP3-K$_x$NiO$_2$ is worth exploring. Our work should contribute to the\nexploration of strategies and materials required to make practical KIBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 May 2023 14:58:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-09"}
