erties via a synergizing\nlearning capacity to express a set of potentialities embedded in the knowledge\nused in training, via the interplay of universality and diversity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 May 2023 12:30:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
